name: $50 Gift Voucher
description: $50 Gift Voucher Give the gift of learning! The gift voucher will be sent digitally, as a PDF. You can choose to print it or have it sent directly to the recipient. You will need to include the recipient's full name, email address and any message you would like included. Vouchers last for 6 months from the purchase date and can be used to purchase any product in our online shop. And don't forget to visit our marvellous website, Handmaker's Factory! A 100% non-refundable, non-transferable payment is required upon ordering. Please include your phone number when ordering so that if needed we can contact you.
